# Source files
# ============
*           text eol=lf
*.pxd		text
*.py 		text
*.py3 		text
*.pyw 		text
*.pyx  		text

*.cmd       text eol=crlf
*.xml       text=auto

# Binary files
*.db		binary
*.p 		binary
*.pkl 		binary
*.pyc 		binary
*.pyd		binary
*.pyo 		binary

# Note: .db, .p, and .pkl files are associated
# with the python modules ``pickle``, ``dbm.*``,
# ``shelve``, ``marshal``, ``anydbm``, & ``bsddb``
# (among others).